        "headline": "How Automatic Return Routing solves IP overlap",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Automatic Return Routing (ARR) solves the common enterprise challenge of overlapping private IP addresses by using stateful flow tracking instead of traditional routing tables. This userspace-driven approach ensures return traffic reaches the correct origin tunnel without manual NAT or VRF configuration.",
